# Using SpecGate

When a task involves a SpecGate artifact, readiness check, work item, change
request, Context Pack, or delivery review, load `using-specgate` first and follow
its routing to the narrow lifecycle skill. Use the `specgate` CLI for platform
operations. Never treat readiness as approval or silently expand approved scope.
